WEBVTT

00:06:58.265 --> 00:07:02.734
Huanza kufikiri kazi yao haijalishi katika kuendesha mabadiliko.

00:07:02.758 --> 00:07:04.564
Na hilo linapotokea,

00:07:04.588 --> 00:07:06.181
mambo huenda polepole,

00:07:06.205 --> 00:07:07.625
nyufa hujitokeza

00:07:07.649 --> 00:07:09.415
na ukosefu wa ufanisi hunawiri.

00:07:11.171 --> 00:07:12.936
Sasa fikiria na mimi,

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:16.898
kama ulikuwa na mchakato ulibidi kufuata --

00:07:16.922 --> 00:07:18.692
na hukuwa na njia nyingine --

00:07:18.716 --> 00:07:21.763
na utaratibu huu ulikosa ufanisi, ulikuwa tata

00:07:22.461 --> 00:07:23.851
na taratibu mno.

00:07:23.875 --> 00:07:25.099
Ungefanya nini?

00:07:26.482 --> 00:07:29.810
Nadhani unaweza kujaribu
kutafuta mtu mwingine akufanyie hilo jukumu,

00:07:29.834 --> 00:07:32.179
ili tu wafanye kwa niaba yako.